    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This kit contains lockpicks and other tools you need to use the @Compendium[pf1.skills.CCy1fajKKU3K02iQ]{Disable Device} skill. Without these tools, you must use improvised tools, and you take a -2 circumstance penalty on @Compendium[pf1.skills.CCy1fajKKU3K02iQ]{Disable Device} checks.</p>\n<p>Smaller and made of stronger materials than most <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/goods-and-services/hunting-camping-survival-geaR/#TOC-Tools-Thieves-\">thieves' tools</a>, the items in this kit are much easier to conceal. You gain a +4 bonus on @Compendium[pf1.skills.zK0CbvpYLZhTN5Wn]{Sleight of Hand}&nbsp;skill checks to conceal these tools on your body. They otherwise function as masterwork thieves tools (granting a +2 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Circumstance-Bonus\">circumstance bonus</a> on @Compendium[pf1.skills.CCy1fajKKU3K02iQ]{Disable Device}&nbsp;checks). <strong>Source</strong> <a href=\"http://www.opengamingstore.com/collections/all-products/products/ultimate-intrigue-pathfinder-rpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO1134</a></p>",
